{"tid":1720903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣建議 - 一日最衰都係","createTime":"2019-11-14T13:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T04:38:40.000Z","uid":188494,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f497a0272ae593d86c16ad5bd3fc30ddeb0a3b1c","tid":1720903,"uid":188494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"最近落親樓都見d阿伯阿婆阿嬋討論政經大事<br />\n經常會出現&rdquo;一日最衰都係阿邊個邊個&rdquo;既句式，聽落真係極具親和力／感染力<br />\n<br />\n9諗左少少例子：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一日最衰都係林鄭，一早撤回咪唔駛搞到七國咁亂</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一日最衰都係林鄭，應承佢咪搞掂囉，大家先有好日子過</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一日最衰都係警察，明知無用都亂放催淚彈，搞到通街都係致癌物</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一日最衰都係警察，亂開槍射死晒d後生，第時靠邊個養？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一日最衰都係工聯會，六七暴動搞到有樣學樣，而家周圍放火擲汽油彈</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一日最衰都係福建幫，周圍撩事鬥非，搞到d後生學跟佢地私了</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一日最衰都係民建聯，講一套做一套，投票又亂咁投，出賣香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一曰最衰都係港鐵，係又封唔係又封，搞到成日都冇車搭</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好明顯呢d都係事實來<br />\n又比較顯淺易明<br />\n真野唔怕拎出來講呀<br />\n特別係選舉快到鳥</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問冇咩設計/藝術天分，唔知點排版比較draw到attention<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣有冇得諗？</span>"},{"pid":"1766f6d05f0b1717be52d89e39bf416ab0c504a0","tid":1720903,"uid":188494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"up1"},{"pid":"c0